'group_rateclimd'			=>	"When enabling this setting, you will need to specify the total rating of the user's comments and the group to which the user will be automatically transferred when this total rating is set.",
'edit_news_alert'			=>	"This publication is already being edited by the user <b>{name}</b>",
'opt_sys_rnctime'			=>	"Xəbərə baxışın hesablanması üçün səhifədə minimum qalma vaxtı",
'opt_sys_rnctimed'			=>	"In this setting, you specify the user's time in seconds, after which the viewing of this publication from the user will be taken into account. If the user was on the page for less than the specified period, the page view will not be counted. The time is specified in seconds and cannot be less than one second",
'opt_sys_recaptsc'			=>	"The value of Score when using reCAPTCHA v.3:",
'opt_sys_recaptscd'			=>	"This value is used to check the probability with which the user can be a robot when using the reCAPTCHA v.3. This field can take a value from 0 to 1, where, for example, 0.1 means that it is most likely a robot, and 0.9 is most likely a person. You can specify, specify with what probability to skip the user. Recommended value: 0.5",
